item.title: Men’s and Women’s Teams
item.author: Laura Bevis,
item.description: After a sickening 30-3 defeat in the away game that left them shaking (literally), the IC girls skipped merrily along to High Barnet with little expectation from Saturday’s game other than to have a nice time and not get as destroyed as last time they played the Bristol women. After a quick warm-up …
